              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/38490527-annerlee?shelf=war">war</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1716573421" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12174510654314474485">A soldier returns from the Gt War to the small town of Flint (Australia). <br/><br/>Not really a crime thriller in the normal sense. Much deeper. <br/><br/>Gave me an insight into the effect of WW1 on returning soldiers and the families of those who didn&apos;t return. Also the dehabilitating effects of the flu epidemic. Bad times</span>
  <span id="freeText12174510654314474485" style="display:none">A soldier returns from the Gt War to the small town of Flint (Australia). <br /><br />Not really a crime thriller in the normal sense. Much deeper. <br /><br />Gave me an insight into the effect of WW1 on returning soldiers and the families of those who didn't return. Also the dehabilitating effects of the flu epidemic. Bad times</span>
